          &lt;a referrer=&quot;null&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20250620-6905113&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;title&quot; id=&quot;mobile-recommend-articles&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              英军舰驶经台海 解放军东部战区：全程跟监警戒
